column21: Step into this expansive Mesa residence on an R2 lot, offering a generous 2,607 square feet of comfortable living space. On the main level, you will find the primary bedroom with an en suite bathroom, along with an additional full bathroom converted from a half bath in the hallway. Descend to the lower level, which features three more bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Outside, a large patio, private backyard, and balconies beckon for relaxation and entertainment. With its proximity to shopping, schools, and the beach, this location is truly exceptional, making it an ideal primary residence or a great income property.

column21: A truly stunning, recently updated luxury home located in the prestigious Franciscan Villas Community. This exceptional end unit is nestled in the back of the community, offering unparalleled privacy and a one-of-a-kind living experience. As you step into this exquisite property, you'll be captivated by the most exquisite finishes and high-end appliances throughout. The spacious living area boasts large windows that allow plenty of natural light to flow in, complemented by a warm and inviting color scheme that creates a serene and welcoming atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening at home. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line stainless appliances, custom cabinetry, and a large counter perfect for meal prep or casual dining. The luxurious master suite offers a peaceful retreat with its spa-like en suite bathroom featuring a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanity sinks. Additional features of this remarkable property include a private patio, perfect for enjoying Santa Barbara's beautiful weather, and access to community amenities such as a pool, making it the ideal place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to own this one-of-a-kind property in one of Santa Barbara's most sought-after neighborhoods. Schedule a private showing today to experience the luxury and privacy of 3744 Greggory Way for yourself.
